Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.96,0:00:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所．以．啊..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.67,0:00:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過坐遠一點再看了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.14,0:00:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.84,0:00:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.25,0:00:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳妳妳幹嘛穿這樣!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.18,0:00:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公，暑假我們一起去海邊玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.49,0:00:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰要跟妳一起去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.89,0:00:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然老公這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.82,0:00:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是前幾天作夢有夢到我對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢到妳?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.33,0:00:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作夢還會夢到我\N表示我們的關係已經很不錯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.20,0:00:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次被夢到了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.57,0:00:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過是做夢想要我怎樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.84,0:00:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次穿著泳衣被丟耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.35,0:00:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能在一起就覺得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.21,0:00:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使被罵了也還是\N好喜歡好喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.22,0:00:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算一副臭臉\N也依然是那麼迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.22,0:01:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請實現我的願望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.22,0:01:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧 一起來吧\N一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧\N一起來吧 一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.16,0:01:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來 一起來\N一起來 一起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.50,0:01:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一．起．來．吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.24,0:01:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那天以來的悸動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.97,0:01:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論何時都希望能感覺的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.25,0:01:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪裡都只想和你一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.15,0:01:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什麼都好讓人心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.93,0:01:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷入戀愛的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.73,0:01:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都好像魔法師一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.93,0:01:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是微不足道的小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.73,0:01:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以讓人高興起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.44,0:01:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能在一起就覺得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.17,0:01:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使被罵了也還是\N好喜歡好喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.24,0:01:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算一副臭臉\N也依然是那麼迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請實現我的願望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.08,0:02:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧 一起來吧\N一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.25,0:02:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧\N一起來吧 一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.26,0:02:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來 一起來 一起來\N一起來 一起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.23,0:02:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.67,0:02:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情書大混亂!左右為難的戀愛!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.07,0:02:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，太天真了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.08,0:02:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.38,0:02:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣的魅力...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.22,0:02:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是像這樣子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.89,0:02:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個夏天，我會用我的魅力\N和岩城小弟談一段美好的戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.52,0:02:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後成為白雪公主的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.42,0:02:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白雪公主?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.96,0:02:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在王子的親吻之下獲得了奇蹟的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.93,0:02:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白雪公主變成了美麗的王妃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.47,0:02:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟那個一樣\N戀愛是從接吻之後才算正式開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而暑假正是追求愛情的大好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要帶岩城小弟到海邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.61,0:03:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後讓他拜倒在大人的魅力之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.11,0:03:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，莉采兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.04,0:03:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的勝算...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾爹C好厲害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.99,0:03:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，我怎麼會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.59,0:03:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我也要和老公到海邊加油嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!怎麼了怎麼了，這麼突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.70,0:03:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵妳也要加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油...什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暑假啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.27,0:03:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說跟老公在海邊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.28,0:03:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.68,0:03:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有啊跟老公在民宿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.15,0:03:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.16,0:03:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有還有跟老公在海之家...\N(在海邊提供飲食、租借等服務的店)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.60,0:04:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何?小葵想不想也像這樣...咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說到國三的夏天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.95,0:04:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會想到「跟喜歡的人接吻」吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暑假也許是最後的機會了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵妳也有「老公」嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎麼可能有嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.72,0:04:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得不錯的倒是有啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那人叫什麼名字啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶!不要啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我嘛，我會幫妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.36,0:04:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.06,0:04:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵之前幫了我這麼多忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次換我來幫妳寫情書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那，叫什麼名字啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.07,0:04:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可以說出去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.37,0:04:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.24,0:04:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是A班的鳳凰院龍之介同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.71,0:04:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，說出來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.25,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A班的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.08,0:04:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人!他很有名耶，長的很帥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.75,0:04:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誠之介同學的話我是知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.32,0:04:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這個人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之是龍之介同學對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.46,0:04:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，原來如此...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.60,0:05:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「你是照亮我心中的光芒」這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵，寫好了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.78,0:05:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.98,0:05:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...這個\N由、由我交給他嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.29,0:05:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.69,0:05:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，如果真的交給他之後\N進行的很順利的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.49,0:05:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我還是不行啦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這個也讓我來吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向A班GO~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被拿去了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.13,0:05:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.37,0:05:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳳凰院龍之介同學在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦~我鍾愛的少女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，薔薇之進同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.37,0:05:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍之介同學在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.64,0:05:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.94,0:05:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.94,0:05:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道這是她最拿手的笑話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.01,0:05:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話如果我認真的回答她\N豈不是太不解風情了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.39,0:05:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想把這個交給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.95,0:06:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這、這這這這是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.66,0:06:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!是情書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻煩你嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.23,0:06:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊，終於下定了決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.73,0:06:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻又不好意思\N所以才用這麼可愛的手段...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是多麼動人又楚楚可憐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我鍾愛的少女啊\N就趁這份感動尚未褪去之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看妳信裡寫了些什麼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.97,0:06:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.42,0:06:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦，怎麼辦，要是順利的話...\N可以的，可以的，好期待好期待...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.75,0:06:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛鳳凰院好像抓著什麼信\N滿臉通紅的倒下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.86,0:06:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的!?成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.06,0:06:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來就等下個禮拜天\N兩個人第一次約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後發生了很多事\N兩人的感情越來越深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.77,0:06:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的時候就，嗯~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭~那樣太快了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還只是中學生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.34,0:06:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在圖書館看到的書上寫說\N中學生到B的人有97%耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人!B是指什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~A是「熱情的吻」的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那B就是「非常熱情的吻」!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.79,0:07:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭~太激烈了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼才大清早的\N心情就這麼好啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.36,0:07:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天是小葵約會的日子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.03,0:07:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想說他們會進展到什麼地步呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次才沒那麼順利呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.87,0:07:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是B呢，還是C呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.24,0:07:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦，C是什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是「超~級熱情的吻」嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.91,0:07:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先不提那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她知道妳跟鳳凰院之間的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶?啊，啊~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都這個時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.98,0:07:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公，要是小葵的約會\N進行得很順利的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.32,0:07:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就親一下當做獎勵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.19,0:07:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是努力的女孩子\N王子就會給她奇蹟的吻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.69,0:07:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔唷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.83,0:07:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少開玩笑了~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門去了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.84,0:08:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，小葵好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來就沒問題了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍、龍之介同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.58,0:08:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，聖本同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.02,0:08:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那那那個，今、今、今天...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.29,0:08:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是巧呢，妳也有約會嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.29,0:08:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是要跟莉采兒小姐約會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.86,0:08:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.86,0:08:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶~怎麼會怎麼會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.16,0:08:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不是龍之介同學\N而是春團治同學來呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.17,0:08:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵，還是老樣子那麼愛說笑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.80,0:08:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人就是龍之介同學啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.74,0:08:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶~~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，我鍾愛的少女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.94,0:08:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今日就讓我倆快樂地渡過這一天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.81,0:08:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我鍾愛的少女?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是擔心小葵才過來看看的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.82,0:08:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是健忘呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.32,0:08:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是寫了這封火辣辣的情書給我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.82,0:08:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...不是的\N這個是小葵要寫給龍之介同學的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.19,0:08:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘記寫上名字了!\N耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.69,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那、那個...這個...所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個就這樣...加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那，拜拜~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.20,0:09:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心裡只有妳一個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃，那種事我從來沒有考慮過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.71,0:09:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，妳都已經來過我家了\N還稱讚過我的收藏不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.21,0:09:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那段幸福的時光我是絕對不會忘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.35,0:09:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒，這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼回事...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳和龍之介同學做了那些事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.86,0:09:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...不是的...是沒錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.99,0:09:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒跟我說呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃，那個...該怎麼說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.86,0:09:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好過份，我最討厭莉采兒了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，等一下，小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵，等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍之介同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.74,0:09:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳終於記起來了，我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.11,0:09:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵她是真的真的\N很喜歡龍之介同學的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.08,0:09:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常總是很有精神\N甚至比男孩子還堅強的小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.75,0:09:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要一提到龍之介同學\N就變的心跳不止，腳也開始站不穩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣的喜歡你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.09,0:09:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是這麼的喜歡一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.89,0:10:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒有獲得任何的回報\N我想她可能非常的傷心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.26,0:10:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.90,0:10:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以請和小葵交往吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.53,0:10:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那些話，我原封不動的還給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對妳的感情，跟那是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.04,0:10:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我已經有老公了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.14,0:10:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也無法和聖本同學交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.92,0:10:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.29,0:10:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我到底該怎麼辦才好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.06,0:10:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想說如果能讓大家都開心就好了...\N難道是我錯了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.56,0:10:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾爹A、B、C!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有東西要找，請出動飛機吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.17,0:10:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能把被稱為「夢幻小熊內褲」\N的「41's PRlNCESS」帶來給我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖本同學的事我就再考慮看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.64,0:10:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.58,0:10:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會說謊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會帶回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.95,0:10:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「41's PRlNCESS」!?\N不...不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.95,0:11:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.09,0:11:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「41's PRlNCESS」可是\N足以堪稱為夢幻的小熊內褲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.33,0:11:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去英國的登山家史頓布拉克\N曾在埃佛勒斯峰峰頂附近發現它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.33,0:11:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻又不小心弄丟了之後\N它的下落就再也沒有人知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.70,0:11:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在他過世時留下的遺書中有聲明\N只要是發現者即可擁有其所有權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.48,0:11:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在無數登山家的努力探尋之下\N至今依然沒有人能找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，小葵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.18,0:11:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是沒能找到...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒，妳醒了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.36,0:11:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，我還要去找東西...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.73,0:11:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.63,0:11:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我先麻煩莉采兒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.10,0:11:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻對妳發這麼大的脾氣，是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.37,0:11:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我會拿出勇氣來\N自己再努力看看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.64,0:11:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣，妳就再睡一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.75,0:12:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.75,0:12:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做的不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.26,0:12:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就為了幫朋友的忙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.76,0:12:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對妳的評價得改一改了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.23,0:12:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就親一下當作獎勵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.26,0:12:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!妳妳、妳起來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.90,0:12:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.40,0:12:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來嘛，獎勵的親親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.64,0:12:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.77,0:12:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼獎勵的親親啊，白痴!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.67,0:12:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家要獎勵啦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.54,0:12:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳很煩耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親親，親親嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.54,0:12:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要太過份了!我才不會親妳啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.68,0:12:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.56,0:12:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊\N衝啊 衝啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.07,0:12:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊 衝啊\N衝啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.44,0:12:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊 衝啊 衝啊\N老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.81,0:13:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡你了 衝啊衝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.22,0:13:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人和女人真是難以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.45,0:13:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了查清楚我去了圖書館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.29,0:13:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對比他年幼的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.46,0:13:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公是一點興趣也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.70,0:13:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是人家好喜歡他，所以我不會哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.47,0:13:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不氣餒，不逃避，更不會失去勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.61,0:13:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信總有一天春天會到來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.49,0:13:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿出認真的力量，認真的力量向前衝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.13,0:13:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊\N衝啊 衝啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.50,0:13:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊 衝啊\N衝啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.00,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊 衝啊 衝啊\N老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.37,0:14:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡你了 衝啊衝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶，又是我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.85,0:14:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥?跟莉采兒相處一段時間後\N感覺如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.65,0:14:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙總是以她的方式在努力著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那點我是很稱讚她啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.52,0:14:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊，這可不代表我承認\N跟那傢伙結了婚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.03,0:14:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶，又是我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們還真閒啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥?跟莉采兒相處一段時間後\N感覺如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.27,0:14:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.80,0:14:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子，說煩人是很煩人啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.17,0:14:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，那傢伙總是\N以她的方式在努力著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.04,0:14:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那點我是很稱讚她啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.04,0:14:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃，或許是我的錯覺也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.55,0:14:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊，這可不代表我承認\N跟那傢伙結了婚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.32,0:14:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(次回 夏天!大海! 目標是傳說\N之吻!?)這點你們可先別搞錯啦
